A version of '''[[Minecraft Indev]]''' was released on '''February 11, 2010''', at 23:33 UTC<ref name=":0">[[#logs|IRC logs]]: "(18:33:12) <Evil-Ville> Notch do you have any idea why it's crashing for me now?"..."(18:33:45) <Notch> try now, Evil-Ville"</ref>. It was announced, bundled with [[Java Edition Indev 20100211-2327|the previous version]], on [[The Word of Notch]] at 23:37 UTC<ref>[[wordofnotch:384494353|Day/night cycle in indev!]] – The Word of Notch, February 11, 2010</ref>.

This version attempted to fix the game crashing<ref name=":0" />, but this fix is unsuccessful.<ref>{{cite IRC log|Adura|date=February 11, 2010|tz=standard|file=2010-02-11_#minecraft.log|"(18:33:57) <Dysafk> I get a white screen in /indev/"..."(18:34:06) <Evil-Ville> still crashes"}}</ref>
This version therefore has no changes at all.
